{"tid":1519740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共司法討論","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:46:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:01:33.000Z","uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a261621688725c2c8dce5cb749cf1aa469ec57a8","tid":1519740,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:46:40.000Z","msg":"見到有手足問「香港法官點諗？」其實呢個問題係之前7百幾位手足被捕同起訴已經有呢個疑問，小弟亦有啲諗法。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 香港司法系統有冇能力處理咁龐大數量既案件？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家講緊9xx +位手足被捕同起訴，加埋今日既大濫捕，個數只會愈黎愈多。梁天琦既暴動罪都唔係一時三刻就搞掂，黃毓民既普通襲擊罪都審咗幾年先玩完。而家講緊隨時上千既案件，我想知香港法庭需要幾多時間去處理？如果講緊單單案都用年去計，隨時香港局勢已經唔知變成點。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 香港法官點諗</span></span><br />\n當然，法官當中不乏紅底/離地撚，佢地會樂意咁做，亦有唔少會歸邊。但始終法治係香港一國兩制既其中一個指標，而家司法獨唔獨立，有冇法制唔係大法官去講，唔係大律師去講，唔係公民黨既人去講，係美國人決定。<br />\n<br />\n而家香港政府擺明濫捕，濫用司法程序，雙重標準咁執法，即使法官秉公辦理，不偏不倚咁去做，其實都係做緊幫凶，其實到最後都係不義。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 大濫捕解決唔到問題，係解決香港自己</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個完全就係港共濫權淪為暴政既表現，要記得香港既地位唔係大陸比既，碗飯係國際比既，呢種變相破壞香港司法既做法，其實都係一種攬炒。<br />\n<br />\n各位手足唔好灰心，今次千載難逢既機會，香港人第一次面對支共去到呢個階段，内憂外患都齊哂，天時地利人和都齊哂，我地一定要堅持落去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f86b8e984a45e0a0edf75ed3921e6ce504a028","tid":1519740,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:52:31.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0gqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=62ff9c4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0gqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=0bffc9e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0gqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=fcff2422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三罷 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fhkgeneralstrike9293&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0gqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=ad2473b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293</a></span>"},{"pid":"bf29be98f988189f6f24a8cead68557c625bb69a","tid":1519740,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:01:33.000Z","msg":"冇人有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}